name: Zelda Zine 1
description: Volume 1 of 3: Wisdom 32 pages of fan-submitted art, design, illustration, and literature. Featuring contributions by Rexbox, Zac Gorman, Madéleine Flores, Maré Odomo, Mathew Kumar, and many more. Curated & edited by Cory Schmitz, Lee Nicholls, GameCity for GameCity6 videogame festival, Nottingham, UK. Collected and compiled 23.10.11 - 28.10.2011 Check out the About page for more images. www.coryschmitz.com www.gamecity.org GameCity is a project of Nottingham Trent University.
